Interface ReactionEventActionBuilder<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the result type
    All Superinterfaces:
    EventActionBuilder<net.dv8tion.jda.core.events.message.react.GenericMessageReactionEvent,T>, EventActionBuilderExtension<net.dv8tion.jda.core.events.message.react.GenericMessageReactionEvent,T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ReactionEventActionBuilderImpl

    public interface ReactionEventActionBuilder<T>
extends EventActionBuilderExtension<net.dv8tion.jda.core.events.message.react.GenericMessageReactionEvent,T>
    This is an extension of EventActionBuilder. Note: using condition(java.util.function.Predicate) will overwrite any conditions already set, which is all of these extension methods.

        Description copied from interface: EventActionBuilder
        Sets a Function that runs after the stopper is called with the Event as the parameter, producing an Object. This allows the EventActionFuture to return a Result when it finishes waiting for events.

        By default, the finisher produces null as a result.
